          "type": "faq",
          "settings": {
            "question": "How long will it take for order to arrive?",
            "answer": "<p>Currently, orders can take 1-4 business days to process before shipping. From there, shipping times are dependent upon location. Check out our shipping page for more information on when to expect your package.</p>"
