        "faq_4rJFEz": {
          "type": "faq",
          "settings": {
            "question": "How do I track my order?",
            "answer": "<p>Once your order ships, you’ll receive a separate email providing you with a tracking number to track your order.* Sometimes this email gets sorted into spam or promotions folders, so be sure to take a look in there if it feels like you’ve been waiting a little too long.</p>"
